<plot>Jason Newman is dying of lung cancer and spends his days waiting for the end. One night, he meets a man with an unusual offer. He will hunt Jason until sundown in a secret location. If Jason survives, he'll get anything he wants. If he's caught, the Hunter will put a bullet in his head. With nothing left to lose, Jason agrees. He soon finds himself in the middle of a field, surrounded by nothing but wilderness and no sign of civilization. The hunt is about to begin...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?521621</url></doc>
